Czech Cabinet May Increase Retail Bond Offering, Lidove Reports

-- B y   P e t e r   L a c a
-- 
2011-10-04T06:44:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/czech-cabinet-may-increase-retail-bond-offering-lidove-reports.html
The Czech government may increase the
first installment of state bonds sold to citizens after about
half of the initial 10 billion-koruna ($531 million) offering
was taken up yesterday,  Lidove Noviny  reported, citing Finance
Minister Miroslav Kalousek.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Peter Laca in Prague at 
